<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contactus.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/todoicon.ico">
    <title>Contact us</title>
</head>
<body> 
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a> Hello <%= firstname %></a>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/TODO">Task Hub</a>
        <a href="/join-room">Join room</a>
        <a href="/addUser">Add user </a>
        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="contact-main-top">
        <img src="/img/sign.png" alt="design-element" class="sign1">
        <header class="main-text">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <p>We value your feedback and inquiries. Whether you have a question about our features or suggestions for improvement, your voice matters to us. Please fill out the contact form below, and we will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        </header>
        <img src="/img/sign.png" alt="design-element" class="sign2">
    </div>

    <section class="contact-us">   
        <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="contact-form">
                <form action="#">
                    <div class="email-phone">
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email">
                        <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Mobile Number">
                    </div>

                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Full Name">
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Message"></textarea>

                    <button type="submit">Submit Button</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            
            <div class="newsletter">
                <h3>Contact Purpose</h3>
                <p>This section of our website is designed to facilitate seamless communication between users and our team. Whether you need assistance with technical issues, wish to provide feedback, or have suggestions for new features, we're here to help. This section also caters to inquiries about collaboration opportunities, business partnerships, or advertising queries. Feel free to reach out for any support or questions!</p>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-info">
        <div class="info-card1">
            <div class="sides">
                <img src="/img/call.png" alt="Phone Icon" class="info-img">
                <h3>(+91) 9695368103</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Call us anytime for assistance or inquiries. Our team is available to help you 24/7.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card2">
            <div class="sides">
                <img src="/img/mail.png" alt="Email Icon" class="info-img">
                <h3>vanshusaxena2208@gmail.com</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Send us an email with your questions or feedback, and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card3">
            <div class="sides">
                <img src="/img/location.png" alt="Location Icon" class="info-img">
                <h3>Gurgaon, Haryana</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Visit our office at this iconic location. We're open Monday to Friday, 9 AM to 6 PM.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="mapouter">
          <div class="gmap_canvas">
            <iframe 
              class="gmap_iframe" 
              frameborder="0" 
              scrolling="no" 
              marginheight="0" 
              marginwidth="0" 
              src="https://maps.google.com/maps?width=1200&height=450&hl=en&q=gurgaon, mg road&t=&z=16&ie=UTF8&i
              wloc=B&output=embed">
            </iframe>
            <a href="https://sprunkin.com">Sprunki Mods</a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
    <div class="rectangle">
        <p>random box to check width</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>